Package linefit.IO

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HasDataToSave
    This interface should be used for classes and objects that have data that should be saved in the LineFit file.
    HasOptionsToSave
    This interface should be used for classes and objects that have options that should be saved in the LineFit file.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChangeTracker
    A class that keeps track of whether or not the file has been modified in such a way that the save file would be different then when it was last saved (i.e.
    ExportIO
    This class Handles all of the export functionality of LineFit including JPG, PDF, and LaTex.
    GeneralIO
    This class Handles the general IO operations of LineFit so that the rest of the code does not need to worry about handling these operations
    LineFitFileIO
    This class Handles reading and saving LineFit data files so that the rest of the code does not need to know the precise format of the data file.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CloseDialogException
    An Exception so we can deal better with closing dialogs and not exploding.
